"Ku-Google+, uzokuba neprofayela yomphakathi ukuze usize abangani bakho ukuthi bakuthole ku-inthanethi. Noma ubani owazi i-imeyili yakho angayithola bese ebuka iprofayiela yakho.

Uma wabelana ngezithombe ku-Google+, abazitholayo nabo bangabelana nanoma ubani omunye. Ukusetheka kokubonakala kwe-albhamu yakho ngeke kuguquke, futhi ungakwenza kube nomkhawulo nganoma isiphi isikhathi ukuze kungabelwana umathanda.
